{"id":289007,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-西安数百购房户到陕西省政府上访请愿（/","date":"2013-04-14T07:45:37Z","modified":"2013-04-14T07:45:37Z","title":"维权网 | 西安数百购房户到陕西省政府上访请愿（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员于富民报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，数百西安领汇双河湾小区的购房户到陕西省政府上访请愿，要求政府发挥职能，督促地产公司尽快复工。以下是他们的请愿声明：</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><b><span>西安领汇双河湾小区的购房户省政府上访请愿书：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></b></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>我们是西安领汇双河湾小区的购房户，我们交了购房款三四年了，最迟的交房日期是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月，但是到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月，只给交付了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>栋楼，而且没水、没天然气、没有硬化道路，其它楼房的施工在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年七八月就停了，现在连塔吊等施工设备也早已拆除运走了，因为拖欠施工方款项太多且时间太长，施工队曾堵了小区大门。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>领汇双河湾小区位于西安北郊八家村，宣传说占地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>多亩，要建数十栋住宅楼，五证齐全，现已预售出三千多套，开发方是辰功地产集团，老板已经换了几个了。听说是开发商把资金挪用，在西安西门外、南郊等处抢购土地了。此项目与后来出了名的陕北神木“房姐”龚艾艾有关。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>我们数百人到西安市政府上访已经三次了，到西安浐灞管委会上访多次，浐灞管委会答复说要责成辰功地产集团尽快复工，最迟要在今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日前复工，但到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>，一点复工的迹象都没有。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>号，数百购房户堵了小区旁边的湖滨路，警察、城管等上百人到现场殴打驱赶我们，打伤七八个人，把五个人抓到派出所，后来放了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>号上午，数百名购房户到陕西省政府上访，要求政府发挥职能，督促尽快复工。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">                   </span><span>领汇双河湾全体购房户</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">                     2013<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">年</span></span>4<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span></span>8<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日</span></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></span></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-4sgnAGfsW5U/UWozL6EGxgI/AAAAAAAAgVI/2K7lLmIvDLw/s1600/DSCN3539.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-4sgnAGfsW5U/UWozL6EGxgI/AAAAAAAAgVI/2K7lLmIvDLw/s400/DSCN3539.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></span></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}